# Files
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
What is file? 
Files are name location on disk to store information
They are used to store data permanently
Data is stored in non-volatile memory
We can retrive data whenever required
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Types of Files?
Text Files : Stores data in the form of Characters. It is used to store data and strings.
eg: .txt file, Json file

Binary Files : Stores data in the form of bytes (group of 8-bits)
eg: audio file, video file, image file, pdf file.
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
What is File Handling?
File Handling Means:-
- Opening a file
- Performing some Operations on it
- Closing a file
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

